<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='9515:9542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0051', 'WYG', '119-22a' );" name="119-22a" class="pb">[119-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
